sentences: Jimmy Needham (born August 22, 1985) is an American contemporary Christian musician signed to Inpop Records.

He released debut album, For Freedom, an independent release, in 2005, and after signing with the Christian record label Inpop in 2006, a series of albums: Speak (2006), Not Without Love (2008),  Nightlights (2010),  Clear the Stage (2012), and Vice & Virtue (2015).
